00:26:00,110 --> 00:26:01,610
is ripping open an old scab,

542
00:26:01,612 --> 00:26:03,912
and this whole trip was a mistake.

543
00:26:05,548 --> 00:26:07,783
His dad was a disaster,

544
00:26:07,785 --> 00:26:09,851
