656
00:32:13,810 --> 00:32:15,077
So much.

657
00:32:15,102 --> 00:32:21,473
♪

658
00:32:21,532 --> 00:32:23,966
[BREATHES SHARPLY]

659
00:32:23,968 --> 00:32:25,634
Can I hug you?

660
00:32:25,636 --> 00:32:32,674
♪

