We can just sit.

745
00:38:41,431 --> 00:38:44,165
Or, um, go for a walk.

746
00:38:48,804 --> 00:38:54,609
I'm... tired.

747
00:38:57,913 --> 00:38:59,413
I should go to sleep.

748
00:39:03,151 --> 00:39:04,418
Okay.

749
00:39:14,596 --> 00:39:16,030
